calendarData.summary: Liip Talk: OK Klima (former Climate Ticker)
calendarData.description:
Liip Talk by Sustainability Lunch
https://www.ok-klima.ch/

Climate protection starts locally: in your community and in your canton. They have important levers to achieve a global impact.

OK Klima shows how you can effectively activate these levers. This is how you accelerate the path to net zero. We carry out a transparent and independent assessment of the climate policy of large Swiss municipalities and cantons and derive suggestions for concrete measures from this.

Transparency, collaboration and citizen participation are at the heart of this project.

calendarData.summary: Sustainability Lunch @FR with OK Klima (former Climate Ticker)
calendarData.description:
Next week ThursdayLiip Talk // 11:30

OK Klima (NPO project) evaluates and compares local climate strategies and empowers citizens. They present their project to us.


Sustainability Lunch:pousse: // 12 – 1pm
In our Sustainability Lunch we look at the local climate strategy at the different Liip locations. Is there a climate strategy available? What kind of documents can we find? Do we understand the information available? How ambitious is it? 
And: Let’s compare the different locations.

Bonjour à tous

Si l'heure ne convient pas, merci de me le dire afin que nous puissions trouver une autre date.

https://track.liip.ch/articles/PHARMACAP-A-4

Meilleures salutations
Adi

---

Le Sprint Review:
Pendant l'événement, la Scrum Team et les parties prenantes passent en revue ce qui a été accomplidurant le Sprint et ce qui a changé dans leur environnement. Sur la base de ces informations, lesparticipants collaborent sur la marche à suivre et sur les décisions à prendre.

Source: https://scrumguides.org/docs/scrumguide/v2020/2020-Scrum-Guide-French.pdf
